    "title": "Is the 50/30/20 Rule Still Realistic in 2025?",
    "description": "Learn how the 50/30/20 budgeting rule works in today's economy, when it fits your lifestyle, and how to adjust it for rising costs and current market conditions.",
    "slug": "50-30-20-budget-rule",
