    "title": "Debugging the Holiday Hangover: Managing Post-December Debt in 2026",
    "description": "Post-holiday debt can feel heavy, but it doesn’t have to come with guilt. This article focuses on understanding December spending, building financial awareness, and starting 2026 with clarity and self-compassion.",
    "slug": "debugging-holiday-debt-2026",
